<view class="page">
  <view class="header-area">
    <view class="title-group">
      <view class="title-en">SERVICE CENTER</view>
      <view class="title-cn">服务中心</view>
    </view>
    <view class="header-glow"></view>
  </view>

  <view class="dashboard-grid">
    
    <view class="grid-col-left card-hover" bindtap="previewQr">
      <view class="card-inner wx-bg-gradient">
        <view class="card-top">
          <view class="icon-halo bg-green-light">
            <image class="card-icon" src="/assets/wechat.png" mode="aspectFit" />
          </view>
          <view class="live-tag">
            <view class="live-dot"></view> Online
          </view>
        </view>
        
        <view class="qr-area-large">
          <view class="qr-frame">
            <image
              wx:if="{{qrSrc}}"
              class="real-qr-large"
              src="{{qrSrc}}"
              mode="aspectFit"
              lazy-load="{{true}}"
              show-menu-by-longpress="{{true}}"
              binderror="onQrImgError"
            ></image>
          </view>
          <view class="qr-tip">长按识别二维码添加客服</view>
        </view>

        <view class="card-bottom-area">
          <view class="wx-label">在线专属客服</view>
          <view class="wx-sub">一对一极速响应</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="grid-col-right">
      
      <view class="small-card phone-card-small card-hover">
        <view class="row-between">
          <view class="info-col">
            <text class="card-label">电话客服</text>
            <text class="card-sub">Phone Support</text>
          </view>
          <view class="icon-halo bg-gold-light scale-sm">
             <image class="card-icon" src="/assets/service.png" mode="aspectFit" />
          </view>
        </view>
        
        <view class="phone-bottom">
          <view class="phone-num-sm din-font">{{phone}}</view>
          <view class="btn-call" catchtap="callPhone" hover-class="btn-call--hover" hover-stay-time="80">拨打</view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="small-card time-card">
        <view class="row-between">
          <view class="info-col">
            <text class="card-label">服务时间</text>
            <text class="card-sub">Service Hours</text>
          </view>
          <view class="icon-halo bg-blue-light scale-sm">
             <image class="card-icon" src="/assets/store.png" mode="aspectFit" />
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="time-txt">
          <view wx:for="{{serviceHoursLines}}" wx:key="index" class="time-line din-font">{{item}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>

    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="faq-section">
    <view class="section-header">常见问题 FAQ</view>
    
    <view class="faq-card">
      <view class="faq-item">
        <view class="q-row">
          <view class="q-icon">Q</view>
          <text class="q-text">配送费如何计算？怎么免配送费？</text>
        </view>
        <view class="a-row">
          <text class="a-text">外卖/快递可能收取配送费，达到门槛可免配送费；结算页会显示配送费及“还差￥xx免配送费”的提示（以商家配置为准）。</text>
        </view>
      </view>


      <view class="divider"></view>

      <view class="faq-item">
        <view class="q-row">
          <view class="q-icon">Q</view>
          <text class="q-text">优惠券怎么领/怎么用？为什么不可用？</text>
        </view>
        <view class="a-row">
          <text class="a-text">进入【我的-优惠券】在“领券中心”领取；结算页选择优惠券即可抵扣。未满足“满xx可用”门槛或订单金额变化时会提示不可用。</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="divider"></view>

      <view class="faq-item">
        <view class="q-row">
          <view class="q-icon">Q</view>
          <text class="q-text">会员等级如何升级？95折什么时候生效？</text>
        </view>
        <view class="a-row">
          <text class="a-text">会员等级按累计充值自动升级（Lv1/2/3/4），升级礼包优惠券会自动发放到【我的-优惠券】；达到 Lv4 后下单自动享受【95折】（结算页会显示会员折扣）。</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="divider"></view>

      <view class="faq-item">
        <view class="q-row">
          <view class="q-icon">Q</view>
          <text class="q-text">积分怎么获得？积分礼品怎么兑换/核销？</text>
        </view>
        <view class="a-row">
          <text class="a-text">订单支付成功后按实付金额获得积分（向下取整）；在【我的-积分】兑换礼品后会生成核销码，到店出示核销码即可核销。</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="divider"></view>

      <view class="faq-item">
        <view class="q-row">
          <view class="q-icon">Q</view>
          <text class="q-text">如何申请售后/退款？退款退到哪里？</text>
        </view>
        <view class="a-row">
          <text class="a-text">在【订单详情】点击【申请售后】提交原因（订单完成后3天内可申请）；可在【售后详情】查看进度或在审核中取消。余额支付会退回余额；微信支付按微信退款流程原路退回，到账时间以微信为准。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
